message:

title: Added granularity to logging flags, so different logging levels can be turned on independently.
message:
Added granularity to logging flags, so different logging levels can be turned on independently.
This is useful as the Market can report crashes with logs, so for release-versions the debug logging can be stripped off, but the other levels can be kept to track the bugs.

title: - Fix for issue 1:
message:
- Fix for issue 1:
  The widgetLayout attributes removed from manage_client.xml, because it caused crashes
  on Motorola Milestone and possibly also on other Motorola phones.
  The widgetLayout also seemed to display incorrectly, if for running the application
  there was used other API-level than the one used for build.
  So for better stability and consistent theme, the widgetLayout parts were removed.
- The About dialog text was updated:
  Reference to AndroBOINC homepage replaces BOINC homepage.
  License is also referenced.
